        <div class="text-center mb-8">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            Hey, I get it. You're a small business owner running your restaurant, and creating a website feels like just another expense you can't afford. But here's the truth: <strong>73% of diners check out a restaurant's website before deciding where to eat</strong>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            If your site is slow, outdated, or—worse—non-existent, you're literally sending customers to the big chain restaurants down the street.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xl text-red-800 leading-relaxed font-bold">
            That's where I come in. I specialize in creating affordable, stunning, mobile-optimized websites specifically for small business restaurants like yours. No generic templates that look like every other place. No confusing tech jargon. Just a beautiful site that helps your small restaurant compete and win.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
