        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-red-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-red-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M3 21h18" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M5 21V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h10a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <path d="M9 21v-6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
              <path d="M8 9h.01M12 9h.01M16 9h.01" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Online Ordering System Setup</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">Want to compete with the big chains offering delivery? I integrate user-friendly online ordering directly into your website—no third-party fees eating into your slim margins. Keep more profit in your small business.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-red-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-red-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
              <path d="M2 12h20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" />
              <path d="M12 2c3 3 4.5 6.5 4.5 10S15 19 12 22c-3-3-4.5-6.5-4.5-10S9 5 12 2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Local SEO Optimization</h3>
          <p class="text-black text-lg leading-relaxed">I optimize your small business restaurant website so you show up when locals search "restaurants near me" or "best [your cuisine] in [your city]." More local visibility = more customers walking through your door.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-orange-50 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-orange-100 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Zap className="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">Fast Loading Speed</h3>
