        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Target className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">I Understand Small Business Challenges</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">I've worked with dozens of small business restaurant owners. I know you don't have unlimited budgets like corporate chains. That's why I offer affordable packages designed specifically for small restaurants that need big results without breaking the bank.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Award className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">No Cookie-Cutter Templates</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Your small business restaurant is unique. I don't use cheap templates that make you look like every other place. I create custom designs that tell your story and make you stand out in your community.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-600 to-red-700 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <TrendingUp className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">I Focus on What Matters: Getting You Customers</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">Pretty designs are nice, but what really matters is bringing people through your door. Every website I build for small business restaurants is designed with one goal: convert visitors into paying customers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-6 group hover:bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <Clock className="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-black">Fast Turnaround</h3>
              <p class="text-black font-medium">I know you need results yesterday. Most small business restaurant websites are completed within 2-3 weeks, so you can start attracting customers fast.</p>
